The Fibonacci sequence is a series of numbers where a number is the addition of the last two numbers, usually starting with 0 and 1.

## Bug Analysis

The bug in the developer's code is likely due to incorrect base cases for the Fibonacci sequence or incorrect implementation of the spiral drawing logic.

