# Debugging Fibonacci Spiral on Canvas

Below is a self-contained HTML file that demonstrates both the buggy and corrected versions of the Fibonacci spiral.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Debugging Fibonacci Spiral</title>
